Package pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1.model

Class Room

java.lang.Object
pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1.model.Room
public class Room extends Object
The Room class represents a hotel room, including information about room number, price per night, capacity, occupancy status, and guest details.
